# VHS tape — Android Frontegg integration demo (CLI fallback for Scene 4)
Output assets/showcase-video-2026-05-04/cli-beat/demo-android.mp4

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1100
Set Height 640
Set Padding 24
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 35ms

Type "npm run demo:android"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 10s
